MORE OF WHAT MATTERS
Celebrating 400 Heart Transplants

The Childrens Heart Center performed its 400th pediatric heart transplant in March 2021.

"We care for some of the sickest and most complicated heart patients. When all other options have failed, we step forward to bring hope to children and their families. 400 times, this program has given children a second chance, and sometimes a third chance, at life.
- Chad Mao, MD, Medical Director of the Advanced Cardiac Therapies Program
